## func Djb33

```go
func Djb33(s string) uint32
```

Djb33 比 FnvHash32 更快的获取字符串哈希值 djb2 with better shuffling. 5x faster than FNV with the hash.Hash overhead. Ref: patrickmn/go\-cache
